headline.0: Prenatal Depression Warning Signs: Here's What to Look For

short_description.0: Until recently, doctors didn't even think a woman could get depressed during pregnancy, because they believed antenatal hormones protected against it. The fact is, as many as 70% of women will experience symptoms of depression during pregnancy.
